    lnoremap √∂ [
    lnoremap √ñ {
    lnoremap √§ ]
    lnoremap √Ñ }
  " Start block with {{
  inoremap {{ {<cr>}<esc>O
  " TODO Erroneously also maps √∂ (small √ñ) to do the same
