" Fzf mappings to search within text (<c-[txv]> to split-open the result)
  " Fzf search lines using \√º, tags using √º
    " In current buffer, or
    " In buffers from buffer list (even unloaded)
    nnoremap √ü :BLines<cr>
    " There is no capital √ü available so use leader instead.
    nnoremap <leader>√ü :Lines<cr>
  " Fzf search for tags
    nnoremap √º :BTags<cr>
    nnoremap √ú :Tags<cr>

