  set list
  set listchars=tab:‚îÇ¬∑ "Use digraph .M for smallest centre dot
  set listchars+=trail:‚ñì " Show trailing spaces cause else its invisible
  set listchars+=nbsp:‚ê£

  "set listchars+=extends:‚Ä¶
  "set listchars+=precedes:‚Ä¶
  set listchars+=conceal:‚îä


  " Overwrite <F3> <F4> mappings in diff mode (for git difftool)
  if &diff
